    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content</head>
      <p>This collection (1863-1932) contains 28 bound volumes and
         two folders of records for the 
         <corpname>Methodist Episcopal Church, South</corpname>, of
         Virginia. The Methodist Church Records are on deposit at the
         University, placed on loan by the Rev. 
         <persname>M. F. Draper</persname>and the Rev. 
         <persname>L. P. Bland</persname>on October 10, 1932 and
         February 15, 1933.</p>
    </scopecontent>
